Package ObjectProject1

Class Table

java.lang.Object
ObjectProject1.Table
public class Table
extends java.lang.Object
A class that makes up a snooker table with rectangles. A table consists of a list of geometries. A table base is built from a group of rectangles. And the legs of the table are made of balls and rectangles.

    • Table

      public Table​(double tableWidth, double tableLength, double holeSize, double edgeWidth, double edgeHeight, double edgeWidth2, double woodWidth, Vector widthVec, Vector lengthVec, Point3D position)
      construct the tableParts. The constructor creates all the geometries that make up it. The constructor starts creating them from the starting point(position) with the directions(widthVec,lengthVec) and sizes(tableWidth,tableLength,holeSize,edgeWidth,edgeHeight,edgeWidth2,woodWidth) of the table.
      Parameters:
      tableWidth - -the table of width
      tableLength - - the table of length
      holeSize - - the size of hole
      edgeWidth - - the edge of width
      edgeHeight - - the edge of height
      edgeWidth2 - -the edge of width2
      woodWidth - -the edge the wood width
      widthVec - - the vector of the width
      lengthVec - - the vector of the length
      position - - The starting point of the table
